    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As with the other issue about supporting console.log, I'm going to close this issue. Geth does not support `evm_setNextBlockTimestamp` and whatnot. Just like with Ethereum, you have to do your testing in Hardhat and then deploy to the production network. This was not possible with OVM 1.0 because of the custom Solidity compiler. This is now 100% possible in OVM 2.0 because it just runs Geth under the hood. ",
